514
00:33:04,140 --> 00:33:05,140
Boo!

515
00:33:05,230 --> 00:33:08,110
- <font color="#ff00ff">[boys laughing]</font>
- Loser.

516
00:33:08,190 --> 00:33:10,980
<font color="#ff00ff">[Will]</font> Mike! Mike!

517
00:34:02,370 --> 00:34:04,290
<font color="#ff00ff">[ringing]</font>

518
00:34:06,710 --> 00:34:09,380
Will, you coming?
Let's go show Mr. Clarke.

519
00:34:10,880 --> 00:34:11,880
What?

