522
00:34:15,880 --> 00:34:18,470
This is the reason I was late for class.

523
00:34:19,390 --> 00:34:21,050
Pretty neat. These doors function?

524
00:34:21,140 --> 00:34:23,510
Well, yeah, obviously.
