00:34:24,890 --> 00:34:27,940
Now, this very well may change
your perception of the world.

527
00:34:28,020 --> 00:34:29,140
Consider my interest piqued.

528
00:34:29,190 --> 00:34:32,320
All right, first,
let's just clarify that...

529
00:34:32,400 --> 00:34:34,650
this is my discovery, not yours.

530
00:34:34,730 --> 00:34:36,070
Dustin, Jesus! Just show him!

531
00:34:36,150 --> 00:34:37,750
- I'm just trying to clarify...
- Dustin!

532
00:34:37,820 --> 00:34:38,990
- Okay, fine.
- <font color="#ff00ff">[door opens]</font>

533
00:34:39,070 --> 00:34:40,070
<font color="#ff00ff">[Mike]</font> Stop!

534
00:34:40,160 --> 00:34:42,200
I'm sorry, Mr. Clarke.
It was just a stupid prank.

535
00:34:42,280 --> 00:34:44,510
- What are you doing?
- I told him to stop. We need to go.

536
00:34:44,540 --> 00:34:46,370
- <font color="#ff00ff">[Dustin]</font> Mike!
- Right now. Right now!

537
00:34:50,750 --> 00:34:52,790
So, your sister coming or what?

538
00:34:54,000 --> 00:34:56,340
Screw it. That little shit can skate home.

539
00:34:58,010 --> 00:34:59,930
- And don't call her that.
- What?

540
00:35:00,010 --> 00:35:02,180
Sister. She's not my sister.

541
00:35:06,560 --> 00:35:09,020
<font color="#ff00ff">[rock music playing loudly]</font>

542
00:35:12,810 --> 00:35:14,440
<font color="#ff00ff">[banging on door]</font>

543
00:35:14,520 --> 00:35:16,440
Hello? Hello?

544
00:35:16,530 --> 00:35:18,780
- Guys, come on. Can I come in yet?
- <font color="#ff00ff">[Mike]</font> No!

545
00:35:19,450 --> 00:35:22,160
- I don't understand.
