00:36:13,790 --> 00:36:15,420
<font color="#ff00ff">[Dart screeching]</font>

572
00:36:18,130 --> 00:36:20,210
Guys, what's going on? Come on.

573
00:36:32,190 --> 00:36:33,700
- Don't hurt him.
