611
00:38:31,600 --> 00:38:32,930
<font color="#ff00ff">[Marsha]</font> Nancy, what is this?

612
00:38:33,010 --> 00:38:35,350
<font color="#ff00ff">[Nancy]</font> I just need you
to trust me. Please.

613
00:38:49,950 --> 00:38:52,070
<font color="#ff00ff">[Owens]</font> Well, you were right
about these pumpkins.

614
00:38:52,160 --> 00:38:53,870
Some nasty stuff.

615
00:38:53,950 --> 00:38:56,080
<font color="#ff00ff">[chuckling]</font> And the smell...
Gee, mother of God.

616
00:38:56,160 --> 00:38:57,720
What exactly do you think
